# Single Server IIS

This template deploys one Windows Server VM with IIS installed.

## Deployed resources

- Virtual network and subnet
- Network security group
- Static public IP address
- Network interface
- Windows Server 2022 Azure Edition VM
- Custom Script Extension to install IIS

## Network access

- RDP TCP/3389 is allowed only from the configured `sourceIpAddress`.
- HTTP TCP/80 is allowed from `webSourceAddressPrefix`. The default value is `Internet`.

## Outputs

- `rdpCommand`
- `websiteUrl`
- `publicIPAddress`
- `privateIPAddress`
